summary: This module customizes the JSON encoding and decoding behavior of Feast protobuf messages, adding special handling for feature list, repeated value, and generic value types. It adapts the protobuf JSON utilities to work correctly with different Feast versions and provides convenient helpers to translate between JSON objects and protobuf instances.
